title: What mains piss you off?
body:
for me my top five are: 
1 Lee Sin mains Vehemently defend one of the most annoying and frustrating champions since his release. 
2 Quinn mains Only a divine power can save you if you suggest anything about Quinn around this delusional lot 
3 Vayne mains Mos Eisley has a nicer population than these people. 
4 Zed mains The most delusional lot I've ever seen 
5 Tryndamere mains. Freelo abusers, freelo abusers, freelo abusers.
